SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781229799
OL,3,CStarmer's authority shaken by defence
OL,4,Csecretary's exit over military funding
OL,6,F"A serious country funds its defence
OL,7,Fto meet the threat it actually faces,
OL,8,Fnot the threat it wishes it faced," he
OL,9,Fadded in his resignation letter.
OL,11,FThe pair are the latest in a series of
OL,12,Fministers who have resigned in the
OL,13,Fcourse of just over a month, following
OL,14,FWes Streeting and a host of junior
OL,15,FGovernment figures who left their
OL,16,Fposts in the wake of Labour's bruising
OL,17,Flocal election defeats in May.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781229799
OL,3,CStarmer's authority shaken by defence
OL,4,Csecretary's exit over military funding
OL,6,FMr Healey and Mr Carns were followed
OL,7,Fout of the door by parliamentary
OL,8,Fprivate secretaries (PPS) Pamela Nash
OL,9,Fand Rachel Hopkins.
OL,11,FTheir exit came even though the
OL,12,Foutgoing defence secretary was
OL,13,Funderstood to have asked that his
OL,14,Fcolleagues in the department remain in
OL,15,Fpost.
OL,17,FNearly nine hours after Mr Healey's
OL,18,Fdeparture, Dan Jarvis was announced by
OL,19,FDowning Street as his successor as
OL,20,FDefence Secretary.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781229799
OL,3,CStarmer's authority shaken by defence
OL,4,Csecretary's exit over military funding
OL,6,FMr Jarvis, a Parachute Regiment
OL,7,Fveteran who has been serving as
OL,8,Fsecurity minister, will now be
OL,9,Fexpected to defend what is expected to
OL,10,Fbe a #13.5 billion uplift in defence
OL,11,Fspending, a figure which military
OL,12,Fchiefs say is far short of what is
OL,13,Fneeded to fund the transformation of
OL,14,Fthe armed forces.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781229799
OL,3,CStarmer's authority shaken by defence
OL,4,Csecretary's exit over military funding
OL,6,FWhile the Government has committed to
OL,7,Fspending 3.5% of GDP on defence by
OL,8,F2035, Mr Healey said the plan he was
OL,9,Fpresented with on Monday moved too
OL,10,Fslowly, with defence spending rising
OL,11,Fto just 2.68% in 2030 after hitting
OL,12,F2.6% next year.
OL,14,FSources said the deal offered by the
OL,15,FTreasury did not put a date on
OL,16,Fincreasing spending to 3%, and had
OL,17,Ftried to force the MoD to plan to only
OL,18,Freach that figure in 2034/35.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
